"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-olympics-2024-imane-khelif-boxing-gender-b1174758.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  OlympicboxerImane Khelifsaid the wave of hateful scrutiny she has faced over misconceptions about her gender \\\"harms human dignity\\\" as she called for an end to \\\"bullying\\\" athletes having been greatly affected by the international backlash against her.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Algerian athlete spoke about her tumultuous Olympic experience on Sunday night in an interview with SNTV, a sports video partner of The Associated Press.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999967222410363, \"rank\": 1.6713008833551858e-06, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9641338983014683, \"rank\": 0.03720033261123239, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I send a message to all the people of the world to uphold the Olympic principles and the Olympic Charter, to refrain from bullying all athletes, because this has effects, massive effects,\\\" Khelif said in Arabic.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It can destroy people, it can kill people's thoughts, spirit and mind.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can divide people.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And because of that, I ask them to refrain from bullying.\\\"\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The victories of Khelif and fellow boxerLin Yu-tingof Taiwan in the ring in Paris have become one of the biggest stories of the 2024Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 3.931265192074248e-11, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.851015987104504e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both women have clinched their first Olympic medals even as they have faced online abuse based on unsubstantiated claims about their gender, drawing them into a wider divide over changing attitudes toward gender identity and regulation in sports.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old Khelif acknowledged the pressure and pain of enduring this ordeal while competing far from home in the most important event of her athletic career.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am in contact with my family two days a week, I hope that they were not affected deeply,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are worried about me.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"God willing, this crisis will culminate in a gold medal, and that would be the best response.\\\"\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The vitriol stems from claims by the International Boxing Association, which has been permanently banned from theOlympics, that both Khelif and Lin failed unspecified eligibility tests for the women's competition at last year's world championships.\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.914528259370798e-30, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif declined to answer when asked whether she had undergone tests other than doping tests, saying she did not want to talk about it.\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She expressed gratitude to the International Olympic Committee and its president, Thomas Bach, for standing resolutely behind her while the banned former governing body of Olympic boxing stoked a furor around her participation in Paris.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2229, \"end\": 2260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2280, \"end\": 2291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 2428, \"end\": 2433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.851015987104504e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games  Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year  Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions  10 great gift ideas that earn you Avios  \\\"I know that the Olympic Committee has done me justice, and I am happy with this remedy because it shows the truth,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2567, \"end\": 2583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also has seen massive support at her bouts, drawing cheers when she enters the arena and crowds waving Algerian flags chanting her first name.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2914, \"end\": 2922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999967222410363, \"rank\": 1.6713008833551858e-06, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will fight again on Tuesday in the women's 66kg semi-finals at Roland Garros.\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif repeatedly made clear she will not allow chatter or accusations to deter her from attempting to claim Algeria's first Olympic gold medal in women's boxing.\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3146, \"end\": 3153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999994354044932, \"rank\": 4.948269395642149e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not care about anyone's opinion,\\\" Khelif said a day afterbeating Anna Luca Hamori of Hungary.\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3272, \"end\": 3276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\", \"score\": 0.9443594635358885, \"rank\": 0.058918807166754544, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\"}, {\"begin\": 3292, \"end\": 3299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.6210478730328577, \"rank\": 0.6039999336511842, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came here for a medal, and to compete for a medal.\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will certainly be competing to improve (and) be better, and God willing, I will improve, like every other athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although she is aware of the worldwide discussion about her, Khelif said she has been somewhat removed.\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3577, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, I do not follow social media,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3579, \"to\": 3630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a mental health team that does not let us follow social media, especially in the Olympic Games, whether me or other athletes.\", \"from\": 3631, \"to\": 3766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am here to compete and get a good result.\\\"\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif started her Olympic run last Thursday with a victory over Angela Carini of Italy,who abandoned the bout after just 46 seconds.\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3878, \"end\": 3891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103664941, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 3895, \"end\": 3900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9894801824533345, \"rank\": 0.010602173727765068, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini later said she regretted her decision and wished to apologize to Khelif.\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 4026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3947, \"end\": 3953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.7285102446893796, \"rank\": 0.3726642930418671, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That unusual ending raised the chatter around Khelif into a roar, drawing comments from the likes of former U.S. President Donald Trump, \\\"Harry Potter\\\" writer J.K. Rowling and others falsely claiming Khelif was a man or transgender.\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4151, \"end\": 4163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999996275619, \"rank\": 3.725143615329303e-10, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 4166, \"end\": 4178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.862648560123923e-14, \"text\": \"Harry Potter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\"}, {\"begin\": 4187, \"end\": 4191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7699732258815184e-35, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC repeatedly declared her and Lin qualified to participate in the Olympics, and it has decried the murky testing standards and untransparent governance of the IBA, which was banished entirely from the Olympics last year in an unprecedented punishment for a governing body.\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4266, \"end\": 4269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0618006572470416e-37, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4427, \"end\": 4430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999400974975, \"rank\": 5.990255033095094e-08, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif clearly felt the weight of the worldwide scrutiny upon her, and her victory over Hamori on Saturday appeared to be cathartic.\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the referee raised Khelif's hand for the win, she went to the centre of the ring, waved to her fans, knelt and slammed her palm on the canvas, her smile turning to tears.\", \"from\": 4675, \"to\": 4851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not control my nerves,\\\" Khelif said in the interview.\", \"from\": 4853, \"to\": 4915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because after the media frenzy and after the victory, there was a mix of joy and at the same time, I was greatly affected, because honestly, it wasn't an easy thing to go through at all.\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 5103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was something that harms human dignity.\\\"\", \"from\": 5104, \"to\": 5147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She had competed in IBA events for several years without problems until she was abruptly suspended from last year's world championships.\", \"from\": 5149, \"to\": 5285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5169, \"end\": 5172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999400974975, \"rank\": 5.990255033095094e-08, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Russian-dominated body - which has faced years of clashes with the IOC - has refused to provide any information about the tests.\", \"from\": 5286, \"to\": 5418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5357, \"end\": 5360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0618006572470416e-37, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Algeria's national boxing federation is still an IBA member.\", \"from\": 5419, \"to\": 5479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5419, \"end\": 5426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999994354044932, \"rank\": 4.948269395642149e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 5468, \"end\": 5471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999400974975, \"rank\": 5.990255033095094e-08, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif is from rural north-west Algeria, and she grew up playing football until she fell in love with boxing.\", \"from\": 5481, \"to\": 5590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5513, \"end\": 5520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999994354044932, \"rank\": 4.948269395642149e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Overcoming her father's initial objections, she traveled 10km by bus to train for fights in a neighbouring town.\", \"from\": 5591, \"to\": 5703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After reaching the sport's top level in her late teens, she struggled early in her career before reaching an elite level.\", \"from\": 5705, \"to\": 5826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif has been a solid, if unspectacular, international competitor for six years, and she lost to eventual gold medalist Kellie Harrington of Ireland at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 5827, \"to\": 6000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5949, \"end\": 5966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kellie Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 5970, \"end\": 5977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.7042928957694814, \"rank\": 0.3754972363613871, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's next bout in Paris is against Janjaem Suwannapheng of Thailand.\", \"from\": 6002, \"to\": 6074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6024, \"end\": 6029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.851015987104504e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Khelif wins again, she will fight for a gold medal on Friday.\", \"from\": 6075, \"to\": 6139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, this issue involves the dignity and honour of every woman and female,\\\" she told an Algerian broadcaster in brief remarks Sunday after beating Hamori.\", \"from\": 6141, \"to\": 6296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6230, \"end\": 6238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999967222410363, \"rank\": 1.6713008833